unk_28bc3c5.value:
function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)

	if not Hydra.ActorIsValid(idPrisoner) then 
		return 
	end
	
	bPrisonerFreed = true
	Hydra.Wait(.25)
	
	if not Hydra.ActorIsValid(idPrisoner) then 
		return 
	end
	
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idPrisoner, ID_WALK_TO_POS, "NPC_Walk", false)
	Hydra.QActorFaceActor(idPrisoner, idActorPlayer)
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(S_CONVERSATION, idPrisoner)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idPrisoner)
	
	if SELECTION == eRunAway then
--		Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(S_POWER_CANNIBAL_BOSS_GRAB, "NO_GRAB", idPrisoner)
		Hydra.QActorAnimAndNewIdle(idPrisoner, "AnimKey_ItemGive_Phased", "AnimKey_Neutral")
		Hydra.Wait(2)
		Hydra.TreasureClassDropAtActorForPlayer(idPrisoner, S_TREASURECLASS, idActorPlayer)
--		Hydra.ActorMergeAIState(idPrisoner, S_AISTATE, idPrisoner, 0)
		Hydra.Wait(1)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idPrisoner, ID_RUN_TO_POS, "NPC_Run", false)
		Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idPrisoner, 1)
	elseif SELECTION == eFollower then
		Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(S_POWER_CANNIBAL_BOSS_GRAB, "NO_GRAB", idPrisoner)
	elseif SELECTION == eHostile then
		Hydra.ActorSetTeam(idPrisoner, Hydra.TEAM_MONSTER_FIRST)
	end
	
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idPrisoner,true)
	Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idPrisoner,false)
	Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idPrisoner,true)
	Hydra.ActorClearAnimSetOverride(idPrisoner)
end

unk_9c63f9d.value:
idPrisoner = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(S_ACTOR_TO_SPAWN, ID_SPAWN_POS, false, 0, 0)
Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idPrisoner,true)
Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idPrisoner,false)
Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idPrisoner,false)
Hydra.ActorSetAnimSetOverride(idPrisoner, "npcM_base_standing_tiedUp_toStake")

unk_28bc3c5.value:
function Start(flGameTime)
	
	if not Hydra.ActorIsValid(idPrisoner) or bPrisonerFreed then 
		return
	end
	
	if bPlayCalloutVO and nTimeToPlayVO<flGameTime then
		Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished("CAMP_Step_Cannibal_Unique_04")
		Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(S_CONV_CALLOUT, idPrisoner)
		nTimeToPlayVO = flGameTime + 15 + (30*Hydra.GetRandomFloat())
	end	
end

-- Event Generic Data

eFollower = "Follower"
eRunAway = "RunAway"
eHostile = "Hostile"
--tEnums = {eFollower, eRunAway, eHostile}
tEnums = {eFollower, eRunAway}
bPrisonerFreed = false
bPrisonerFreed = false
bPlayCalloutVO = false
nTimeToPlayVO = 0

--SELECTION = tEnums[Hydra.GetRandomInt(1, #tEnums)]
SELECTION = eRunAway

S_CONV_CALLOUT = Hydra.ReferenceConversation("CAMP_Step_Cannibal_Prnr_Help")

if SELECTION == eFollower then
	if Hydra.GetRandomInt(1, 2) == 1 then
		S_ACTOR_TO_SPAWN = Hydra.ReferenceActor("CAMP_Step_Cannibal_Prisoner_Follower_M")
	else
		S_ACTOR_TO_SPAWN = Hydra.ReferenceActor("CAMP_Step_Cannibal_Prisoner_Follower_F")
	end
	S_CONVERSATION = Hydra.ReferenceConversation("CAMP_Step_Cannibal_Prnr_Folw")
elseif SELECTION == eRunAway then
	if Hydra.GetRandomInt(1,2) == 1 then
		S_ACTOR_TO_SPAWN = Hydra.ReferenceActor("CAMP_Step_Cannibal_Prisoner_RunAway_M")
	else
		S_ACTOR_TO_SPAWN = Hydra.ReferenceActor("CAMP_Step_Cannibal_Prisoner_RunAway_F")
	end
	S_TREASURECLASS = Hydra.ReferenceTreasureClass("Gizmo_Reward_CorpseAdventurer")
	S_AISTATE = Hydra.ReferenceAIState("EVT_Monster_RunToRandomPosAndFade")
	S_CONVERSATION = Hydra.ReferenceConversation("CAMP_Step_Cannibal_Prnr_RnAw")
elseif SELECTION == eHostile then
	if Hydra.GetRandomInt(1,2) == 1 then
		S_ACTOR_TO_SPAWN = Hydra.ReferenceActor("CAMP_Step_Cannibal_Prisoner_M")
		Hydra.ActorSetIdleAnim(S_ACTOR_TO_SPAWN, "npcM_base_HTH_tiedUpBack_idle")
	else

	end
	S_CONVERSATION = Hydra.ReferenceConversation("CAMP_Step_Cannibal_Prnr_Hstl")
end
